org.batfish.specifier

Interface LocationSpecifierFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AllInterfaceLinksLocationSpecifierFactory, AllInterfacesLocationSpecifierFactory, CaseInsensitiveRegexLocationSpecifierFactory, DescriptionRegexInterfaceLinkLocationSpecifierFactory, DescriptionRegexInterfaceLocationSpecifierFactory, FlexibleLocationSpecifierFactory, NameRegexInterfaceLinkLocationSpecifierFactory, NameRegexInterfaceLocationSpecifierFactory, NodeNameRegexInterfaceLinkLocationSpecifierFactory, NodeNameRegexInterfaceLocationSpecifierFactory, NodeRoleRegexInterfaceLinkLocationSpecifierFactory, NodeRoleRegexInterfaceLocationSpecifierFactory, NodeRoleRegexLocationSpecifierFactory, TypedLocationSpecifierFactory, VrfNameRegexInterfaceLinkLocationSpecifierFactory, VrfNameRegexInterfaceLocationSpecifierFactory

    public interface LocationSpecifierFactory
    A LocationSpecifierFactory is used by Questions to build LocationSpecifier objects. The factory can be responsible for parsing and validating the fields from question input.
